ries`, `writeFlaggedStories`, `removeFlaggedStory` |\n156\t\n157\t## Stream Parsing & Ink Rendering\n158\t\n159\t| File | Purpose | Key Exports |\n160\t|------|---------|-------------|\n161\t| ink-components.tsx | Ink/React terminal UI components — Header, ActiveTool, CompletedTool, LastThought, RetryNotice, StoryBreakdown, StoryMessages, App | `Header`, `App`, `SprintInfo`, `StoryStatusEntry`, `StoryStatusValue`, `StoryMessage` |\n162\t| ink-renderer.tsx | Ink renderer controller — creates/manages Ink instance, exposes RendererHandle for state updates, signal cleanup | `startRenderer`, `RendererHandle`, `RendererState`, `noopHandle` |\n163\t\n164\t## Run Command Helpers\n165\t\n166\t| File | Purpose | Key Exports |\n167\t|------|---------|-------------|\n168\t| run-helpers.ts | Extracted helpers for `run.ts` — elapsed time formatting, sprint status mapping, story counting, line processor | `formatElapsed`, `mapSprintStatus`, `mapSprintStatuses`, `countStories`, `createLineProcessor` |\n169\t\n170\t## Dashboard Formatting\n171\t\n172\t| File | Purpose | Key Exports |\n173\t|------|---------|-------------|\n174\t| dashboard-formatter.ts | Parses ralph's structured output lines and reformats them as a clean dashboard with icons and progress tracking | `DashboardFormatter`, `formatDashboardLine` |\n175\t\n176\t## Issue Tracking\n177\t\n178\t| File | Purpose | Key Exports |\n179\t|------|---------|-------------|\n180\t| issue-tracker.ts | File-based issue tracker — CRUD for `.codeharness/issues.yaml` with auto-generated sequential IDs, status/priority validation | `readIssues`, `writeIssues`, `nextIssueId`, `createIssue`, `closeIssue`, `VALID_STATUSES`, `VALID_PRIORITIES`, `Issue`, `IssuesFile` |\n181\t\n182\t## Dependency Management\n183\t\n184\t| File | Purpose | Key Exports |\n185\t|------|---------|-------------|\n186\t| deps.ts | Auto-install external tools (Showboat, agent-browser, beads, Semgrep, BATS, cargo-tarpaulin) with fallback chains | `DEPENDENCY_REGISTRY`